messages.messageBody:
Dear Group-members,

Please send me as many on-line and off-line informations based on historical
facts (and not beautiful but romantical books) concerning on Musashi's
family - both parents, brothers or sisters, and so on -, and early childhood
period of him.
I wish everibody a Happy New Year!

Thank you for the cooperation!

Gyula
